#index-banner.parallax-container
  .section.no-pad-bot
    .container
      %h1.header.center.blue-grey-text.text-darken4 Let's Contribute
      .row.site_description
        .col.s12
          .card.card-panel.blue-grey.darken-1
            %span.card-title Bored of your daily job ?
            %p
              Lets contribute and make your presence in Open Source community.
              we will show you random open issues on repository related to your choice of language,
      .row.center
        .input-field.black-text
          = text_field_tag :language, nil, class: 'typeahead',  placeholder: 'Which language ?'
      .row.center.blue-grey-text.text-darken4
        %h5 Not sure which language to select ?
      .row.center
        %a.btn-large.blue-grey.waves-effect.waves-light
          I'm feeling Lucky
  .parallax
.container.issue_detail
  = render 'home/issue_detail', issue: @issue, repository: @issue.repository
.parallax-container.valign-wrapper
  .section.no-pad-bot
    .container
      .row.center
        %h5.header.col.s12.light A modern responsive front-end framework based on Material Design
  .parallax
.container
  .section
    / Icon Section
    .row
      .col.s12.m4
        .icon-block
          %h2.center.brown-text
            %i.material-icons flash_on
          %h5.center Speeds up development
          %p.light We did most of the heavy lifting for you to provide a default stylings that incorporate our custom components. Additionally, we refined animations and transitions to provide a smoother experience for developers.
      .col.s12.m4
        .icon-block
          %h2.center.brown-text
            %i.material-icons group
          %h5.center User Experience Focused
          %p.light By utilizing elements and principles of Material Design, we were able to create a framework that incorporates components and animations that provide more feedback to users. Additionally, a single underlying responsive system across all platforms allow for a more unified user experience.
      .col.s12.m4
        .icon-block
          %h2.center.brown-text
            %i.material-icons settings
          %h5.center Easy to work with
          %p.light We have provided detailed documentation as well as specific code examples to help new users get started. We are also always open to feedback and can answer any questions a user may have about Materialize.
.container
  .section
    .row
      .col.s12.center
        %h3
          %i.mdi-content-send.brown-text
        %h4 Contact Us

:javascript
  var languages = #{@languages.to_json}
